sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id", COALESCE("statuses"."reblog_of_id", "statuses"."id") AS status_id FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND ("statuses"."local" = $1 OR "statuses"."uri" IS NULL) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $2

SELECT "mentions"."id", "mentions"."status_id" FROM "mentions" WHERE "mentions"."account_id" IN (SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IS NULL) AND "mentions"."silent" = $1 ORDER BY "mentions"."id" ASC LIMIT $2

SELECT "favourites"."id", "favourites"."status_id" FROM "favourites" WHERE "favourites"."account_id" IN (SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IS NULL) ORDER BY "favourites"."id" ASC LIMIT $1

SELECT polls.id, polls.status_id FROM "polls" INNER JOIN "poll_votes" "votes" ON "votes"."poll_id" = "polls"."id" WHERE "votes"."account_id" IN (SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IS NULL) ORDER BY "polls"."id" ASC LIMIT $1
SELECT "bookmarks"."id", "bookmarks"."status_id" FROM "bookmarks" ORDER BY "bookmarks"."id" ASC LIMIT $1
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" = $1 ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC
